SplitOff: <<
	Package: %N-shlibs
	Depends: glib2-shlibs (>= 2.14.0-1), libiconv, libxml2-shlibs (>= 2.6.30-1), x11-shlibs
	Files: lib/libxklavier.12*dylib share/%N
	Shlibs: %p/lib/libxklavier.12.dylib 13.0.0 %n (>= 3.4-1)
	DocFiles: COPYING* README
<<
DocFiles: AUTHORS COPYING* CREDITS ChangeLog INSTALL NEWS README 
